<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_4c0532c6-743a-4440-8828-b2ae4b0e0300" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I4D24</sptc><title id="_2a3c2633-3e84-4689-b3f2-13ae95ed371f">Seating in rows: platforms and steps</title><archive-num>2019: NSW H101.11.7</archive-num><subclause id="_3702c6d9-69fd-414c-bda4-7090ee4b4d85" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_51d9bc8a-a5a5-4cec-851f-2520ddc08c75">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Where an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2325_1.3.0.xml#_7bd3266d-23ef-465c-a5c4-c548e11fa575" id="_4c0ac03f-05fd-4aaa-ad13-cd6bf3550584" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">aisle</xref> contains platforms or steps—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_05b1342c-e840-40a8-b269-eb4f20abef97">the platforms and steps must extend for the full width of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2325_1.3.0.xml#_7bd3266d-23ef-465c-a5c4-c548e11fa575" id="_accecfc9-5ec7-4852-bdd8-d56464136d91" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">aisle</xref>; and</li><li id="_f933d9ca-8b34-4ba1-9dee-402213b26f48">if there are no intervening steps between levels of platforms, the height of the platform riser must not be more than 200 mm; and</li><li id="_4315aa90-20ac-4a59-a61d-144af5f870dd">if there are one or more intervening steps between the levels of platforms—<ol><li id="_9f701c82-93d1-4be5-af1c-a7af7d5d994f">each riser must be at least 100 mm but not more than 200 mm high; and</li><li>each going must be at least 250 mm deep; and</li><li>risers and goings must be uniform; and</li></ol></li><li id="_e5e10f4e-3324-433c-a724-3c97b7f4f25c">goings which are more than 450 mm deep at platform level must have a grade of not more than 1 in 50; and</li><li id="_150bb6d2-b1bb-45b8-848f-ada5449392d0">at the entrance from the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2325_1.3.0.xml#_7bd3266d-23ef-465c-a5c4-c548e11fa575" id="_64cce6b7-d15c-4fe9-bbff-5b53be374fca" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">aisle</xref> to each <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_c8ae019f-93be-4dcb-9241-c55e7a581867" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">row</xref> there must be a clear level floor space, extending the full width of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2325_1.3.0.xml#_7bd3266d-23ef-465c-a5c4-c548e11fa575" id="_f852c319-ba27-48db-9ff3-aa76b040fc03" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">aisle</xref>, of at least 300 mm, measured from the back of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2458_5.1.0.xml#_0d278c41-777a-48f5-8130-efe976c8bf82" id="_6e3c4e0b-225a-4b53-a965-1c8a1082ad02" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">row</xref> in front; and</li><li id="_55320705-030e-45e5-addb-5296f88ce211">any going projecting in front of a seat adjacent to an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2325_1.3.0.xml#_7bd3266d-23ef-465c-a5c4-c548e11fa575" id="_81663761-1fff-4dd8-a460-49eb7ce5e49e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">aisle</xref> must be protected by a guardrail.</li></ol></subclause></clause>